<figure> also good
  <img src="soup.png" alt="a picture of hot soup">
  <figcaption>a long description of the above soup</figcaption>
</figure>

leave non-meaningful images with blank alt text - if no alt, screen readers would announce the whole image src url
<img src="article-icon.png" alt="">

